## 🛠️ كيفية التشغيل محلياً / How to Run Locally

### 1. المتطلبات / Prerequisites:
* Docker & Docker Compose installed.
* Git installed.

### 2. التشغيل / Deployment:
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone [https://github.com/mwahibelhag/zero-cost-devops-pipeline.git](https://github.com/mwahibelhag/zero-cost-devops-pipeline.git)
cd zero-cost-devops-pipeline

# Run the system with Docker Compose
docker-compose up -d --build  
